Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's... one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.51,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.93,0:00:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where? Where did the sniper shoot from?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.10,0:00:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.38,0:01:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Leave there immediately via route C and await your next instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.09,0:01:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A suspicious bullet that didn't hit anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's see how our heroine will improvice her way through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.28,0:01:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You summon me here and then shoot at me?! What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.13,0:01:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to take responsibility for this, aren't you?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?! Isn't the shooter one of your guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna kill you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Mr. Godo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That surprised me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ray...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W... wanted to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another sniper... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji... Hey Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing... Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:02:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.39,0:03:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My subordinate succeeded in eliminating the threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.86,0:03:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be any more shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of charade is this, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Godo. I hereby present you Isaac Wisemel,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the ringleader of the plot that has endangered you over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I punished the traitor who mislead our organization for his own purposes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Traitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better be ready to explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the reason for killing one of our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To put it simply, Wisemel was responsible for this shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you check the sniper that was taken care of by my subordinate...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that should be hard evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph. How very well prepared you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Inferno's way of taking responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hotel shooting happened after I shot Randy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't Wisemel's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was another sniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was also Wisemel's henchman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was obstinate like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did the shooter stop after one shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.75,0:04:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wisemel's objective was supposedly to eliminate Daisuke Godo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure talk like you're the only one who knows the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether he killed Godo or not... didn't really matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real goal of the sniper was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to fill the minds of those at the meeting with doubts and fears
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and ruffle Inferno from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sniper might have even guessed that Claudia was going to shoot Wisemel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole thing was Wisemel's plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Clo decided to take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fill your head with crazy ideas. We're just pawns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to pry into things that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lizzie's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, if this series of murders was Wisemel's doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where that five million dollars should go is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Godo Family's stolen money is found in Wisemel's vacation home...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, everything will be settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The yakuza's murders... Judy's revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my own selfish speculation as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I heard a rumor... that Isaac of the Bloodies died. Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sniper you shot was one of Isaac's henchmen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it was him who killed Judy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's over... the revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Uhm... How was my training to become an assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like, shall I continue to help you with your assassinations?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about being a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Then I'm no longer needed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd hate to give up that cooking of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can be my maid and do the cooking for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! All right! I'm going to be a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to try being a maid once. The uniform is really cute, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No uniform?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay... as long as you let me stay by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An excellent report.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This whole series of incidents was Isaac Wisemel's scheme...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, the Godo Family will have to accept that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to think that you figured out all this in that chaos...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Isaac is gone I'll have you take his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't disappoint me, Claudia McCunnen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Potential?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. She's got a rare quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can even call it a talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talent... Someone told me a similar thing in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you're saying that you want to train that girl as an assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:08:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't produce results...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the rest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we shall see how you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to put her in any more danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make up some excuses so she can...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feeling at peace these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out. I may not be able to come back until the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've told you this sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay. I'll see you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like administrative work has become completely natural to you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just settle where you are right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're officially a senior member now. You no longer have to push too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What more do you need? Getting too greedy will ruin you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I know there's no way you'd stop no matter what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just make sure you watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:11:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like such a fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me at least give you advice. It's my hobby, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal, I wasn't really sure, but is this the fermented tofu stuff you were talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... welcome home! You're already back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal, where'd you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remembered to buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chicken marinated in this tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay... to go on like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still want to become your assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... that you don't want me to become an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the pain that comes with being an assassin, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to be able to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm weak and poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything without depending on someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to live like that any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal, you can take any path. You can become anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all things, why do you want to become an assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like assassins?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you don't like yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I don't. I ended up becoming a killer and can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already broken. Do you want to be like me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm sorry, Reiji... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal... I was too harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true. I don't know how many have people died because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They would've been able to live on if it wasn't for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.27,0:14:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They would've been able to go back to their loved ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just doing the job that someone has to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then did you want to kill people?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you shoot those people because you wanted to kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like killing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard, stressful, sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't forgive yourself for doing such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you're trying to kill yourself inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a fool who fires away like those who killed Judy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You live bearing the pain of what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't make mistakes. You don't kill people for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were you in that alley that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judy wouldn't have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:15:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once you kill, everything in the world changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scenery you see, the sounds you hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to accept people with a kind heart like you're able to right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to become like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a good place for you to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't come into the same world I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's where you're always going to be, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I go there, I'll be able to be with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be separated from you. I want to be with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be of help to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:16:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could be with you if I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. I'll go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come to your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll go. Let me go back... to the world you live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal... Before I met you, it was as if I were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get separated from you, I'll go back to being that dead person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You helped me remember... how to laugh... and to cry as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Ms. McCunnen was making every effort to get you to join Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when the plan was changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact bro immediately! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your time on the stage will be over soon, Ms. McCunnen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send an appropriate bouquet for your finale.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.14,0:18:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.99,0:18:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom. Hey, can you take a job right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:18:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some remnants of the Bloodies who're acting funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to take care of them without a big fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you give me a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Where do I have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet up at the usual switchyard at 20 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.51,0:19:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping to be with you all day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll always be together from now on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have tons of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get my old self back...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for Elen as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me Elen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.77,0:20:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just Ein... as I always was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.32,0:20:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
